snippet.title: Infinitum: The Backrooms Story | Official Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Kickstarter is planned to launch on 20 december!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/infinitumgame/infinitum-the-backrooms-story

Wishlist here - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2302120/Infinitum_The_Backrooms_Story/
https://linktr.ee/infinitumgame

I had to repost this trailer because the intro part of it was just boring and the quality was worse than expected so I re-rendered it in 4K and made it shorter!

#backrooms #infinitumgame #trailer #indiegame
